{
  "nbformat": 4,
  "nbformat_minor": 5,
  "metadata": {
    "kernelspec": {
      "name": "maxima",
      "display_name": "Maxima",
      "language": "maxima"
    },
    "aximar": {}
  },
  "cells": [
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "# ODE Integration with SUNDIALS CVODE\n\n`np_cvode` wraps the SUNDIALS CVODE solver for initial value problems $\\dot{y} = f(t, y)$.\n\nTwo calling conventions:\n- **Expression mode**: `np_cvode([f1, ...], [t, y1, ...], y0, tspan)`\n- **Function mode**: `np_cvode(f, y0, tspan)` where `f(t, y)` returns a list\n\nSupports Adams (non-stiff, default) and BDF (stiff) methods.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "load(\"numerics\")$\nload(\"numerics-sundials\")$\nload(\"ax-plots\")$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 1,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## 1. Exponential Decay\n\n$\\dot{y} = -y$, $y(0) = 1$. Exact solution: $y(t) = e^{-t}$.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "tspan : np_linspace(0.0, 5.0, 100)$\nresult : np_cvode([-y], [t, y], [1.0], tspan)$\n\nt_col : np_slice(result, all, 0)$\ny_col : np_slice(result, all, 1)$\ny_exact : np_exp(np_scale(-1.0, t_col))$\nprint(\"Max error:\", np_max(np_abs(np_sub(y_col, y_exact))))$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 2,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "Max error: 1.3237647200625702e-8"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "ax_draw2d(\n  color=\"#2563eb\", line_width=2, name=\"CVODE\",\n  lines(t_col, y_col),\n  color=\"#dc2626\", dash=\"dash\", name=\"exp(-t)\",\n  explicit(exp(-t), t, 0, 5),\n  title=\"Exponential Decay\", xlabel=\"t\", ylabel=\"y\",\n  grid=true, showlegend=true\n)$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 3,
      "outputs": [
        {
