          },
          "metadata": {},
          "output_type": "display_data"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## 3. Function Mode\n\nThe same oscillator using a callback function instead of symbolic expressions.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "osc_rhs(t, y) := [np_ref(y, 1), -np_ref(y, 0)]$\n\nres3 : np_cvode(osc_rhs, [1.0, 0.0], np_linspace(0.0, float(2*%pi), 200))$\nnp_shape(res3);",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 7,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "data": {
            "text/latex": [
              "\\left[ 200 , 3 \\right] "
            ]
          },
          "execution_count": 7,
          "metadata": {},
          "output_type": "execute_result"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## 4. Stiff System — Adams vs BDF\n\n$\\dot{y} = -1000\\,y + 3000 - 2000\\,e^{-t}$, $y(0) = 0$.\n\nExact: $y(t) = 3 - 0.998\\,e^{-1000t} - 2.002\\,e^{-t}$.\n\nThe fast transient ($e^{-1000t}$) decays in ~0.01 time units, making this stiff.\nBDF handles this efficiently; Adams needs many more steps.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "tspan4 : np_linspace(0.0, 0.5, 200)$\n\n/* BDF (stiff solver) */\nres_bdf : np_cvode([-1000*y + 3000 - 2000*exp(-t)],\n                   [t, y], [0.0], tspan4, 1e-10, 1e-10, bdf)$\n\n/* Adams (non-stiff) for comparison */\nres_adams : np_cvode([-1000*y + 3000 - 2000*exp(-t)],\n                     [t, y], [0.0], tspan4, 1e-10, 1e-10, adams)$\n\nprint(\"Both methods converge to the same solution\")$\nt4 : np_slice(res_bdf, all, 0)$\ny_bdf : np_slice(res_bdf, all, 1)$\ny_adams : np_slice(res_adams, all, 1)$\nprint(\"Max difference:\", np_max(np_abs(np_sub(y_bdf, y_adams))))$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 8,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "Both methods converge to the same solution\nMax difference: 5.690126148039099e-10"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "/* Exact solution */\ny_exact4(t) := 3 - 0.998*exp(-1000*t) - 2.002*exp(-t)$\n\nax_draw2d(\n  color=\"#2563eb\", line_width=2, name=\"BDF\",\n  lines(t4, y_bdf),\n  color=\"#dc2626\", dash=\"dot\", name=\"Exact\",\n  explicit(y_exact4(t), t, 0, 0.5),\n  title=\"Stiff ODE: BDF Method\", xlabel=\"t\", ylabel=\"y\",\n  grid=true, showlegend=true\n)$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 9,
      "outputs": [
        {
